Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.22,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}We're back with Jim Parsons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:04.98,EN,,0,0,0,,And that was a clip from Jim's new show, {\i1}Call Me Kat{\i0}, which he's producing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.83,EN,,0,0,0,,And joining us is the star of the show, Mayim Bialik.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:08.73,EN,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mayim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:09.44,EN,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.65,EN,,0,0,0,,Hello, Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.99,EN,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you, and it's great y'all are working
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.36,EN,,0,0,0,,together again after {\i1}Big Bang{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:18.02,EN,,0,0,0,,How did this come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:20.00,EN,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:21.81,EN,,0,0,0,,Jim came to me...oh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:23.29,EN,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.18,EN,,0,0,0,,You can say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:26.69,EN,,0,0,0,,I came to you while on set one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.95,EN,,0,0,0,,Well, Jim came to me, and he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:32.40,EN,,0,0,0,,I want to know what you think about this project that my company has.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.71,EN,,0,0,0,,It's this Miranda show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:35.60,EN,,0,0,0,,It was really popular on the BBC.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:36.50,EN,,0,0,0,,And so I went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:38.80,EN,,0,0,0,,I did a little research, and I came back the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.74,EN,,0,0,0,,And I said, well, Jim, that seems
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:41.99,EN,,0,0,0,,like a really awesome project.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:42.95,EN,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:44.77,EN,,0,0,0,,You got my vote of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.76,EN,,0,0,0,,And he said, no, I'm asking because I want you to be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:50.20,EN,,0,0,0,,And I was shocked because I think I'm very annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.37,EN,,0,0,0,,But however annoying I am, he obviously
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:53.77,EN,,0,0,0,,still wanted to work with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:55.99,EN,,0,0,0,,Yes, Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:59.37,EN,,0,0,0,,I think that the annoying quality you bring
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.64,EN,,0,0,0,,is what America responds to, Mayim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:03.60,EN,,0,0,0,,I think that's what this character wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:04.83,EN,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.98,EN,,0,0,0,,That's very relatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:10.22,EN,,0,0,0,,Everyone love, we know someone annoying, so that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:12.81,EN,,0,0,0,,Tell everybody what the show is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:16.86,EN,,0,0,0,,Jim, you want me to take this one, or you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:18.39,EN,,0,0,0,,Well, you're working on it, so please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:19.01,EN,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:24.02,EN,,0,0,0,,This is a show about a 39-year-old single woman who
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.63,EN,,0,0,0,,does not have the life that society often says
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:28.39,EN,,0,0,0,,39-year-old women should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:30.24,EN,,0,0,0,,But she's happy anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:31.57,EN,,0,0,0,,She has an exciting career.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:33.54,EN,,0,0,0,,She just opened a cat café
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:35.24,EN,,0,0,0,,yes, a cat café.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:38.67,EN,,0,0,0,,And we have some amazing, amazing guest stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:41.41,EN,,0,0,0,,We have Swoosie Kurtz playing my mom, and Leslie Jordan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:43.94,EN,,0,0,0,,and Cheyenne Jackson, Kyla Pratt, and Julian Gant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:48.05,EN,,0,0,0,,And we're just having a blast making this show about a very,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.33,EN,,0,0,0,,very quirky woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.63,EN,,0,0,0,,She's sloppy. She's messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:51.84,EN,,0,0,0,,She's sometimes vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.27,EN,,0,0,0,,She's socially anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:55.48,EN,,0,0,0,,I don't wear Spanx in real life, so she doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.76,EN,,0,0,0,,have to wear Spanx either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.03,EN,,0,0,0,,And that's a really good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.11,EN,,0,0,0,,And you work with a lot of cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.31,EN,,0,0,0,,You already, you have three cats, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:04.44,EN,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:08.02,EN,,0,0,0,,I am a cat person, and my character is as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:10.38,EN,,0,0,0,,We like to say, she's not a sad cat lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.93,EN,,0,0,0,,She's a rad cat lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.45,EN,,0,0,0,,But you have... I mean, I just,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:19.19,EN,,0,0,0,,I look at that, and I think, you know cats, I know cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:20.59,EN,,0,0,0,,They usually don't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:23.56,EN,,0,0,0,,So how do these actor cats all of a sudden meet each other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:26.35,EN,,0,0,0,,and not get into these cat fights?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.76,EN,,0,0,0,,OK, so here's the thing about our cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:31.90,EN,,0,0,0,,And I should say, I'm a vegan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:35.16,EN,,0,0,0,,And so I was very, very pleased we
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.32,EN,,0,0,0,,do not have cats that are tethered or drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.49,EN,,0,0,0,,These are just real cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.86,EN,,0,0,0,,Many of them are the Ragdoll breed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.85,EN,,0,0,0,,which is a breed that literally likes to chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:47.19,EN,,0,0,0,,And these cats are raised as kittens
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:50.37,EN,,0,0,0,,to be around other people and other cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.90,EN,,0,0,0,,The exception is a cat named Piper,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.42,EN,,0,0,0,,who played Firework, who did not like to be around other cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.49,EN,,0,0,0,,So we had to kind of block for Piper special.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:01.23,EN,,0,0,0,,So Piper didn't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.50,EN,,0,0,0,,Piper's audition didn't work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:06.75,EN,,0,0,0,,Well, Piper just had to be in scenes just with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.85,EN,,0,0,0,,and Piper didn't really care for me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.78,EN,,0,0,0,,But Piper looked like a firework.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:11.88,EN,,0,0,0,,We worked around that diva.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.91,EN,,0,0,0,,It's amazing what we'll do in Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:15.76,EN,,0,0,0,,We'll put up with anything if you got the right look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:16.48,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.29,EN,,0,0,0,,Even with cats, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.52,EN,,0,0,0,,That's taking it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.98,EN,,0,0,0,,And you have not been to the set, Jim,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:29.18,EN,,0,0,0,,because of your COVID.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.68,EN,,0,0,0,,But also, you're allergic to cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.82,EN,,0,0,0,,So how…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:33.53,EN,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.03,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how did you decide to produce a show
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:38.16,EN,,0,0,0,,about a bunch of cats knowing you're going
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.64,EN,,0,0,0,,to have to visit that set?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.97,EN,,0,0,0,,It's the only way he could plan to work with me, if he never
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:42.94,EN,,0,0,0,,had to be around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.49,EN,,0,0,0,,Because I'm so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.58,EN,,0,0,0,,No, no. I'll tell you honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.91,EN,,0,0,0,,I kind of didn't think of...well, first of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.11,EN,,0,0,0,,while we were proposing it, Darlene Hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.88,EN,,0,0,0,,who is running the show, she placed it in the cat cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.16,EN,,0,0,0,,The original Miranda wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.12,EN,,0,0,0,,And so I didn't realize this nightmare was going
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:00.34,EN,,0,0,0,,to take place in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:04.51,EN,,0,0,0,,However, there was one time very early on in {\i1}Big Bang{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.63,EN,,0,0,0,,where, at one point, they were tossing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.09,EN,,0,0,0,,around that idea for a script.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.56,EN,,0,0,0,,And they came up and asked me, are you allergic to cats,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.23,EN,,0,0,0,,by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.36,EN,,0,0,0,,And I said, yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:14.52,EN,,0,0,0,,My eyes get puffy and whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.73,EN,,0,0,0,,About a week later, the script showed up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.47,EN,,0,0,0,,with a box of Claritin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:20.81,EN,,0,0,0,,And it was like, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.15,EN,,0,0,0,,We're going to do one where you're surrounded
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.56,EN,,0,0,0,,by cats the whole episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.24,EN,,0,0,0,,And Mayim was actually there for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.01,EN,,0,0,0,,So I have gone through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:29.13,EN,,0,0,0,,And if I don't touch my face, like I keep
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:30.69,EN,,0,0,0,,doing right now... there I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.25,EN,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.10,EN,,0,0,0,,But I didn't. I was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.94,EN,,0,0,0,,I just didn't touch my face. So…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:36.97,EN,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.05,EN,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that they knew you were allergic to cats
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.04,EN,,0,0,0,,and wrote an episode with you surrounded by cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:42.59,EN,,0,0,0,,I just…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.94,EN,,0,0,0,,They asked me a few seasons later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:51.76,EN,,0,0,0,,if I could ride a unicycle, and I nearly had a digestive issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:52.60,EN,,0,0,0,,And I said, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.59,EN,,0,0,0,,Because I thought, oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:54.37,EN,,0,0,0,,They're going to make me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.84,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm going to crack my skull open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.61,EN,,0,0,0,,That's just how they roll around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:04:59.63,EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.09,EN,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:05.60,EN,,0,0,0,,That's one of Portia's goals is to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.02,EN,,0,0,0,,how to ride a unicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:09.48,EN,,0,0,0,,She's really interested in unicycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.27,EN,,0,0,0,,She's never…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.00,EN,,0,0,0,,I imagine it takes a lot of core strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.52,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it takes a lot of core strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.84,EN,,0,0,0,,She got a three-cycle instead of a unicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.55,EN,,0,0,0,,And she rides a three-cycle around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.79,EN,,0,0,0,,Have you seen those?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:20.90,EN,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.68,EN,,0,0,0,,I only know it as a tricycle from when I was a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.23,EN,,0,0,0,,I don't think I know what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.14,EN,,0,0,0,,It's like that, but you just sit upright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:30.50,EN,,0,0,0,,And there's three things, and you have to still balance it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.00,EN,,0,0,0,,But it's… anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:35.42,EN,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.00,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm just... when I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.51,EN,,0,0,0,,We should cut to a clip, this is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.34,EN,,0,0,0,,Well, it's called{\i1} Call Me Kat{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.19,EN,,0,0,0,,It airs Thursdays at 9:00 on Fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.46,EN,,0,0,0,,And great talking to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:49.75,EN,,0,0,0,,Stay safe, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:50.96,EN,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.70,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}All right, we'll be right back.
Comment: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,CN,,0,0,0,,--------------------TEXT-CN--------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.22,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}我们回来了和吉姆·帕森斯一起
Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.22,0:00:04.98,CN,,0,0,0,,那是吉姆正在出演的新剧《叫我凯特》的一个片段
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.83,CN,,0,0,0,,加入我们的是这个节目的明星，马伊姆·拜力克
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.83,0:00:08.73,CN,,0,0,0,,嗨，马伊姆
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.73,0:00:09.44,CN,,0,0,0,,你好吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.65,CN,,0,0,0,,你好，你好
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.99,CN,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你，很高兴你们在生活大爆炸
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.36,CN,,0,0,0,,之后又一起工作了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.36,0:00:18.02,CN,,0,0,0,,这是怎么发生的？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.80,0:00:20.00,CN,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.00,0:00:21.81,CN,,0,0,0,,吉姆来找我...哦，你继续
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.51,0:00:23.29,CN,,0,0,0,,不，不
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.18,CN,,0,0,0,,你先说
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.18,0:00:26.69,CN,,0,0,0,,有一天我来找你
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.95,CN,,0,0,0,,吉姆来找我，他说
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.95,0:00:32.40,CN,,0,0,0,,我想知道你对我们公司这个项目的看法
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.71,CN,,0,0,0,,这是米兰达的剧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.71,0:00:35.60,CN,,0,0,0,,它在BBC上真的很受欢迎。
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.60,0:00:36.50,CN,,0,0,0,,所以我回家之后
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.50,0:00:38.80,CN,,0,0,0,,我做了点调查，第二天回来之后
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.74,CN,,0,0,0,,我说，吉姆，看来
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.74,0:00:41.99,CN,,0,0,0,,这是一个非常棒的项目
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.99,0:00:42.95,CN,,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.95,0:00:44.77,CN,,0,0,0,,你得到了我的信任
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.76,CN,,0,0,0,,他说，不，我问你是因为我想让你参与进来
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.76,0:00:50.20,CN,,0,0,0,,我很震惊因为我觉得我很烦人
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.37,CN,,0,0,0,,但不管我多么烦人，他显然
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.37,0:00:53.77,CN,,0,0,0,,还想和我一起工作
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.20,0:00:55.99,CN,,0,0,0,,是的，吉姆？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.99,0:00:59.37,CN,,0,0,0,,我以为你烦人的性格
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.64,CN,,0,0,0,,是美国人特有的回应，马伊姆
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.64,0:01:03.60,CN,,0,0,0,,我想这就是这个角色需要的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.31,0:01:04.83,CN,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.98,CN,,0,0,0,,这是与其息息相关的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.98,0:01:10.22,CN,,0,0,0,,每个人都被喜爱，我们需要认识一个让人讨厌的人，所以这是完美的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.74,0:01:12.81,CN,,0,0,0,,告诉大家这个剧是关于什么的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.69,0:01:16.86,CN,,0,0,0,,吉姆，你是想让我回答来这个，还是你来？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.86,0:01:18.39,CN,,0,0,0,,噢，你正在出演这个剧，当然是你来回答
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.39,0:01:19.01,CN,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.76,0:01:24.02,CN,,0,0,0,,这是一部关于一个39岁的单身女人的剧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.63,CN,,0,0,0,,她没有过着社会常说的那种
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.63,0:01:28.39,CN,,0,0,0,,39岁的单身妇女应该有的标志性的生活
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.39,0:01:30.24,CN,,0,0,0,,但她还是很开心
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.24,0:01:31.57,CN,,0,0,0,,她有一份令人兴奋的事业
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.57,0:01:33.54,CN,,0,0,0,,她刚开了一家猫咖啡馆
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.54,0:01:35.24,CN,,0,0,0,,是的，猫咖啡馆
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.57,0:01:38.67,CN,,0,0,0,,我们有一些了不起的来宾
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.67,0:01:41.41,CN,,0,0,0,,我们有史洛希·库尔特扮演我的母亲，还有莱斯利·乔丹
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.41,0:01:43.94,CN,,0,0,0,,还有夏安·杰克逊，凯拉·普拉特和朱利安·甘特
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.94,0:01:48.05,CN,,0,0,0,,我们开心的完成了这个剧关于一个非常
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.33,CN,,0,0,0,,非常古怪的女人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.63,CN,,0,0,0,,她草率，她混乱
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.63,0:01:51.84,CN,,0,0,0,,她有时粗俗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.27,CN,,0,0,0,,她也有社交焦虑
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.27,0:01:55.48,CN,,0,0,0,,我在现实生活中不穿塑身衣，所以她也
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.76,CN,,0,0,0,,也不非得穿塑身衣
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.03,CN,,0,0,0,,这是一件好事
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.11,CN,,0,0,0,,你和很多只猫一起工作
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.31,CN,,0,0,0,,你已经有三只猫了，对吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.67,0:02:04.44,CN,,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.44,0:02:08.02,CN,,0,0,0,,我是一个猫人，我的角色也是如此
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.02,0:02:10.38,CN,,0,0,0,,我们常常说，她不是一个悲伤的猫咪夫人
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.93,CN,,0,0,0,,她是个疯狂的猫夫人。
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.45,CN,,0,0,0,,但你有，我的意思是，我只是，
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.45,0:02:19.19,CN,,0,0,0,,我看了看，我想，你了解猫，我也了解
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.19,0:02:20.59,CN,,0,0,0,,它们通常一个人呆着
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.59,0:02:23.56,CN,,0,0,0,,那么这些猫演员是如何相遇
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.56,0:02:26.35,CN,,0,0,0,,并且不会发生打架之类的事的？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.76,CN,,0,0,0,,好吧，这是关于我们猫的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.20,0:02:31.90,CN,,0,0,0,,我得说，我是素食主义者
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.90,0:02:35.16,CN,,0,0,0,,所以我非常非常高兴我们的猫
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.32,CN,,0,0,0,,没有被绑住或下药
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.49,CN,,0,0,0,,这些是真正的猫
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.86,CN,,0,0,0,,其中许多是布偶猫这个品种
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.85,CN,,0,0,0,,这是一个喜欢放松的品种
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.85,0:02:47.19,CN,,0,0,0,,这些猫是从小猫一起长大的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.19,0:02:50.37,CN,,0,0,0,,和其他人和其他猫一起
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.90,CN,,0,0,0,,例外的是一只叫派珀的猫
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.42,CN,,0,0,0,,它总是容易与其他的猫有火花，并且不喜欢和其他猫在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.49,CN,,0,0,0,,所以我们不得不为派珀设置一些障碍
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.91,0:03:01.23,CN,,0,0,0,,所以派珀没做到吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.50,CN,,0,0,0,,派珀的试镜没成功？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.09,0:03:06.75,CN,,0,0,0,,好吧，派珀只是需要和我在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.85,CN,,0,0,0,,派珀也不是很在乎我
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.78,CN,,0,0,0,,但派珀像是烟花
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.78,0:03:11.88,CN,,0,0,0,,我们在那个女主角身边工作过
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.91,CN,,0,0,0,,这是在好莱坞我们做的最神奇的事
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.91,0:03:15.76,CN,,0,0,0,,如果你的三观正，我们会忍受一切的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.76,0:03:16.48,CN,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.29,CN,,0,0,0,,即使是对猫来说，你也是对的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.52,CN,,0,0,0,,这太过分了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.98,CN,,0,0,0,,而且你还没去过现场，吉姆
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.98,0:03:29.18,CN,,0,0,0,,因为你那儿的新冠疫情
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.68,CN,,0,0,0,,并且你对猫过敏
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.82,CN,,0,0,0,,所以怎么...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.82,0:03:33.53,CN,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.03,CN,,0,0,0,,是啊，你是怎么决定出演这个剧的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.03,0:03:38.16,CN,,0,0,0,,当你知道那儿会有一群猫
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.64,CN,,0,0,0,,并且你不得不去那个片场的时候？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.97,CN,,0,0,0,,这是他唯一能和我一起工作的方法，如果他从来没有
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.97,0:03:42.94,CN,,0,0,0,,必须在我身边
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.49,CN,,0,0,0,,因为我太烦人了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.58,CN,,0,0,0,,不，不。 我老实告诉你
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.91,CN,,0,0,0,,我没想到…首先
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.11,CN,,0,0,0,,当我们提议的时候，达琳·亨特
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.88,CN,,0,0,0,,在主持这个节目，她把它的地点设置在猫咖啡馆里
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.16,CN,,0,0,0,,原来的米兰达不是这样的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.12,CN,,0,0,0,,所以我没有意识到我的噩梦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.12,0:04:00.34,CN,,0,0,0,,将会以这种方式发生
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.34,0:04:04.51,CN,,0,0,0,,然而，在生活大爆炸里很早就有一次
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.63,CN,,0,0,0,,在某一时刻，他们在提出
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.09,CN,,0,0,0,,关于着剧本的想法
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.56,CN,,0,0,0,,他们上来问我，你对猫过敏吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.23,CN,,0,0,0,,在任何情况下？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.36,CN,,0,0,0,,我说，是的，是的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.36,0:04:14.52,CN,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛会浮肿等等
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.73,CN,,0,0,0,,大约一周后，剧本出现了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.47,CN,,0,0,0,,和一盒氯雷他定（治疗过敏症状用）一起
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.47,0:04:20.81,CN,,0,0,0,,就像，我们在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.15,CN,,0,0,0,,我们要在你被包围的环境里做一个
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.56,CN,,0,0,0,,由猫组成的整个情节
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.24,CN,,0,0,0,,而马伊姆实际上就在那里
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.01,CN,,0,0,0,,所以我经历了那件事之后发现
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.01,0:04:29.13,CN,,0,0,0,,如果我不碰我的脸，就像我一直这样
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.13,0:04:30.69,CN,,0,0,0,,现在做...我在那儿
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.25,CN,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.10,CN,,0,0,0,,但我没有过敏，我很好
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.94,CN,,0,0,0,,我只是没碰我的脸。 所以…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.94,0:04:36.97,CN,,0,0,0,,哇哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.05,CN,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信他们知道你对猫过敏
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.04,CN,,0,0,0,,还让你一起拍摄被猫包围的剧情
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.04,0:04:42.59,CN,,0,0,0,,我只是...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.14,CN,,0,0,0,,好吧，我告诉你
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.94,CN,,0,0,0,,他们几季之后问我
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.94,0:04:51.76,CN,,0,0,0,,如果我能骑独轮车，我几乎无法消化这个问题
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.76,0:04:52.60,CN,,0,0,0,,我说，不
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.59,CN,,0,0,0,,因为我想，哦，天哪
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.59,0:04:54.37,CN,,0,0,0,,他们会让我这么做的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.84,CN,,0,0,0,,我简直快要精神失常
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.61,CN,,0,0,0,,他们就是在打这样的主意
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.66,0:04:59.63,CN,,0,0,0,,哦，你不能？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.09,CN,,0,0,0,,好吧，祝你好运
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.39,0:05:05.60,CN,,0,0,0,,波西亚的目标之一就是学习
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.02,CN,,0,0,0,,如何骑独轮车
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.02,0:05:09.48,CN,,0,0,0,,她对独轮车很感兴趣
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.27,CN,,0,0,0,,她从不...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.00,CN,,0,0,0,,我想这需要很多核心力量
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.52,CN,,0,0,0,,是的，这需要很大的核心力量
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.84,CN,,0,0,0,,她得到了一辆三轮车，而不是独轮车
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.55,CN,,0,0,0,,她骑着三轮车转圈
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.79,CN,,0,0,0,,你看过那些吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.27,0:05:20.90,CN,,0,0,0,,不管怎样
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.68,CN,,0,0,0,,我小时候就只知道它是三轮车
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.23,CN,,0,0,0,,我不知道这是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.14,CN,,0,0,0,,就像那样，但你只能坐直了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.14,0:05:30.50,CN,,0,0,0,,而且有三个东西，你仍然需要保持平衡
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.00,CN,,0,0,0,,但是…无论如何
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.92,0:05:35.42,CN,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.00,CN,,0,0,0,,我只是…当我听到你的声音时
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.51,CN,,0,0,0,,我们应该把这段剪掉，这太疯狂了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.34,CN,,0,0,0,,好吧，这部剧叫做《叫我凯特》
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.19,CN,,0,0,0,,星期四上午9点在福克斯播出
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.46,CN,,0,0,0,,很高兴和你们聊天
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.46,0:05:49.75,CN,,0,0,0,,注意安全，好吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.00,0:05:50.96,CN,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.70,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}好的，我们马上回来
